                A magical mirror, a terrible enemy, and one boy unravelling the
                secret behind his legacy.
            </p>

            <div
                class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start pt-6"
            >
                <a
                    href="#book"
                    class="px-8 py-3 bg-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-primary/90 text-white font-medium rounded uppercase tracking-wider text-sm transition-all shadow-sm"
                >
                    About The Book
                </a>
                <a
                    href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09N7JRBL1/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="px-8 py-3 bg-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-primary/90 text-white font-medium rounded uppercase tracking-wider text-sm transition-all shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
                >
                    <svg
